{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"4437d6a687","title":"关于上海失守后救亡运动的方针问题的指示","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"40b239aee1","index":0,"year":1937,"month":11,"day":12,"articleId":"4437d6a687"}],"tags":[{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji11","name":"毛泽东全集第11卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji11.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji11":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"567d9f2365","type":"paragraph","text":"关于上海失守后救亡运动的","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji11","articleId":"4437d6a687"},{"id":"24dd5265f4","type":"paragraph","text":"方针问题的指示","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji11","articleId":"4437d6a687"},{"id":"4b143e7cf5","type":"paragraph","text":"（1937年11月12日）博、潘、刘：甲、上海失去后，上海教亡运动必将更为困难。公开数亡团体应准备必要时转入秘密状态。党的秘密工作亦应有新的布置。严防敌人的突然袭击。乙、上海失去后，救亡运动中心将转移至武汉。因此党的与非党的干部，亦应重新分配。一部分应去武汉，一部分去战区，一部分环境较好的仍留下。工作方式应召（有）必要的转变内、汉年兄及省委所在地问题，待周博来此后再决定，汉年兄应完全秘密起来。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji11","articleId":"4437d6a687"},{"id":"d09d67875d","type":"paragraph","text":"洛毛","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji11","articleId":"4437d6a687"},{"id":"69a2ef1e1d","type":"paragraph","text":"十一月十二日[1]这是毛泽东和洛甫（张闽天）二人给博古（秦邦完）、潘汉年和刘晓的指示电。","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji11","articleId":"4437d6a687"}],"page":{"id":"7c11c679b5","publicationId":"maoquanji11","articleId":"4437d6a687","start":386,"end":386}}}},"__N_SSG":true}